Minimum Moves to Equal Array Elements III
---

## ðŸ§  Time and Space Complexity:
- **Time Complexity:** O(n)
- **Space Complexity:** O(1)

---

## âœ… Full Solution:
*/

class Solution {
    public int minMoves(int[] nums) {
        int n = nums.length;
        int max = nums[0];
        
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            max = Math.max(nums[i], max);
        }
        
        long ans = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            ans += (max - nums[i]);
        }
        
        return (int) ans;
    }
}
